dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Washington County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Washington_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
